data.description: **Short Sale in process- The property is to be sold in present condition** This wonderful 2 bedroom, 2 bath split floorplan home is waiting for you. The original owner home sits at the end cul-de-sac with a large lot and is steps away from Granite Falls Golf Course. It can be updated into a 3 bedroom by converting the optional office back into a bedroom. The 3 car garage has been used as a workshop with plenty of custom cabinet storage while maintaining room for cars or golf carts. New Roof installed in March 2023 right before going on market.
